WEBVTT

00:00.001 --> 00:01.793
<i>Previously on "Bitten".</i>

00:01.818 --> 00:03.429
- Who is out there?
- The Wolf.

00:03.469 --> 00:04.969
The one who betrayed you.

00:05.004 --> 00:06.984
- Where is he?
- He's with her.

00:07.008 --> 00:08.375
The she-wolf.

00:08.410 --> 00:09.809
Elena, I am your father.

00:09.837 --> 00:11.411
I'm tired of being attacked.

00:11.446 --> 00:12.612
This is the course I've chosen.

00:12.648 --> 00:13.813
We're going to stick to it.

00:13.848 --> 00:15.682
Now this Pack will be strong.

00:15.717 --> 00:17.583
This is how we will restore order.

00:17.618 --> 00:18.785
I hate this.

00:18.820 --> 00:20.586
I have been tracking

00:20.621 --> 00:23.790
a very dangerous Russian Mutt for years.

00:23.825 --> 00:25.658
I believe he is in North America.

00:25.693 --> 00:27.626
Sasha Antonov.

00:27.662 --> 00:29.295
I've never heard that name.

00:29.330 --> 00:30.863
The name Antonov
comes with a heavy price.

00:30.899 --> 00:32.765
It affects my children as well,

00:32.801 --> 00:34.533
so we've been living in hiding

00:34.568 --> 00:37.303
with Katia, Alexei, all of their lives.

00:37.338 --> 00:39.672
Today, the name of
Escobado comes to an end.

00:39.707 --> 00:41.440
Let Roman take the prize.

00:41.475 --> 00:43.676
Buy his friendship with my head.

